           Build-Depends:       QuickCheck >= 2.3 && < 2.5

           Exposed-Modules:     Data.GraphViz.Testing
                                Data.GraphViz.Testing.Instances
                                Data.GraphViz.Testing.Properties

           Other-Modules:       Data.GraphViz.Testing.Instances.FGL
